against Napoli Matfia.

726
00:30:06,971 --> 00:30:09,974
There's a city named Aosta
in northern Italy,

727
00:30:10,041 --> 00:30:11,776
very famous for cheese.

728
00:30:11,843 --> 00:30:14,078
There's a dish called valdostana,

729
00:30:14,145 --> 00:30:17,048
which tops steak
or other protein with cheese.

730
00:30:17,115 --> 00:30:20,318
I'm going to make valdostana

731
00:30:20,385 --> 00:30:23,288
