and creamy dish for Won-young.

732
00:30:23,354 --> 00:30:24,923
-I see.
-Yes.

733
00:30:24,989 --> 00:30:26,958
His explanation already sounds great.

734
00:30:27,025 --> 00:30:28,359
-Does it?
-Yes, I love it.

735
00:30:28,426 --> 00:30:29,427
-Just by words?
-Yes.

736
00:30:29,494 --> 00:30:31,329
I prepared

737
00:30:33,431 --> 00:30:36,367
