Do you have to fry them that much?

1806
01:13:02,144 --> 01:13:03,879
Did you want the colors to change
to burn them?

1807
01:13:03,946 --> 01:13:05,547
Come and try some.

1808
01:13:05,614 --> 01:13:07,015
"Come and try some."

1809
01:13:07,082 --> 01:13:08,517
