01:13:29,371 --> 01:13:30,372
-My gosh.
-You know,

1817
01:13:30,439 --> 01:13:32,040
-they're both…
-That was exquisite.

1818
01:13:32,107 --> 01:13:34,676
-They're both delicate.
-They're moving at similar speeds.

1819
01:13:35,811 --> 01:13:37,613
