1820
01:13:37,679 --> 01:13:39,581
When they used endives, they both did.

1821
01:13:39,648 --> 01:13:42,151
When they use fruit, they both use fruit.

1822
01:13:42,217 --> 01:13:43,419
My gosh.

1823
01:13:43,485 --> 01:13:45,053
-You have five minutes.
-Five minutes.

1824
01:13:45,120 --> 01:13:47,823
You have five minutes left.
You should start wrapping up.

1825
01:13:47,890 --> 01:13:49,892
Hold your breath, love dining.

1826
01:13:49,958 --> 01:13:51,193
Totally.

1827
01:13:51,260 --> 01:13:52,461
I'll go to this side.

