-What about her health?

1869
01:15:27,556 --> 01:15:29,091
We'll all taste it anyway.

1870
01:15:29,157 --> 01:15:30,359
It tastes burnt.

1871
01:15:30,425 --> 01:15:31,493
But it's good.

1872
01:15:31,560 --> 01:15:33,362
-Burnt yet tasty.
-Burnt yet tasty.

1873
01:15:33,428 --> 01:15:34,429
Burnt yet tasty.

1874
01:15:35,130 --> 01:15:38,333
THE RIB EYE STEAK IS DONE RESTING

