1877
01:15:48,176 --> 01:15:50,145
CHEF SON JONG-WON
SERVES HIS SECOND DISH

1878
01:15:52,281 --> 01:15:54,516
-Now, 3 minutes and 50 seconds.
-Yes.

1879
